#: en/home-router-howto.xml:106
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"If you do not see your two cards showing up and you're not sure what kind of\n"
"cards you have, try running <c>lspci | grep Ethernet</c>.  You can get that\n"
"from <c>emerge pciutils</c>.  Once you have this information, go into your\n"
