"この情報をもとに、適切なドライバのサポートをカーネルに追加しましょう。\n"

#. type: Content of: <guide><chapter><section><body><p>
#: en/home-router-howto.xml:113
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"The next thing you'll need is support for iptables and NAT (and packet shaping\n"
"if you want).  The following list is split up into always required (*),\n"
"required only for adsl via PPPoE (a), suggested for everyone (x), and only\n"
"for shaper (s) features.  It does not matter whether you build the features\n"
